WEBVTT

00:00:06.919 --> 00:00:17.519
Long is my night ♪ its burden, too heavy ♪ 

00:00:13.520 --> 00:00:30.400
Worn down, yet with my Lord, no despair ♪ 

00:00:26.401 --> 00:00:39.000
Flaws weigh on my soul ♪ sins chain my heart ♪

00:00:35.001 --> 00:00:45.320
Return, O soul ♪ repent from the wandering ♪ 

